juniRadiusInitiatedRequestMIB.name: juniRadiusInitiatedRequestMIB

revisions.description: Initial version of this MIB module, derived from IETF Informational Rfc 3576.

juniRadiusInitiatedRequestMIB.contactinfo: Juniper Networks, Inc. Postal: 10 Technology Park Drive Westford, MA 01886-3146 USA Tel: +1 978 589 5800 Email: mib@Juniper.net
juniRadiusInitiatedRequestMIB.description: The RADIUS Disconnect MIB for the Juniper Networks enterprise.

juniRadiusInitiatedRequestInvalidClientA.name: juniRadiusInitiatedRequestInvalidClientAddresses
juniRadiusInitiatedRequestInvalidClientA.description: The number of RADIUS initiated request packets received from unknown addresses.

juniRadiusInitiatedRequestClientTable.name: juniRadiusInitiatedRequestClientTable
juniRadiusInitiatedRequestClientTable.description: The (conceptual) table listing the RADIUS authentication servers with which the ERX shares a secret.

juniRadiusInitiatedRequestClientEntry.name: juniRadiusInitiatedRequestClientEntry
juniRadiusInitiatedRequestClientEntry.description: An entry (conceptual row) representing a RADIUS initiated request client with which the server shares a secret.

juniRadiusInitiatedRequestClientAddress.name: juniRadiusInitiatedRequestClientAddress
juniRadiusInitiatedRequestClientAddress.description: The IP address of the RADIUS client referred to in this table entry. A value of 0.0.0.0 indicates this entry is not in use.

juniRadiusInitiatedRequestClientPortNumb.name: juniRadiusInitiatedRequestClientPortNumber
juniRadiusInitiatedRequestClientPortNumb.description: The UDP port the server is listening on to recieve disconnect requests from this client.

juniRadiusInitiatedRequestUnknownTypes.name: juniRadiusInitiatedRequestUnknownTypes
juniRadiusInitiatedRequestUnknownTypes.description: The number of RADIUS packets of unknown type which were received from this client on the authentication port.

juniRadiusInitiatedRequestNoSecret.name: juniRadiusInitiatedRequestNoSecret
juniRadiusInitiatedRequestNoSecret.description: The number of RADIUS Disconnect requests recieved from this client while no secret is set.

juniRadiusInitiatedRequestDisconnectRequ.name: juniRadiusInitiatedRequestDisconnectRequests
juniRadiusInitiatedRequestDisconnectRequ.description: The number of RADIUS Disconnect packets received from this client.

juniRadiusInitiatedRequestDisconnectAcce.name: juniRadiusInitiatedRequestDisconnectAccepts
juniRadiusInitiatedRequestDisconnectAcce.description: The number of RADIUS Disconnects that were succesful.

juniRadiusInitiatedRequestDisconnectReje.name: juniRadiusInitiatedRequestDisconnectRejects
juniRadiusInitiatedRequestDisconnectReje.description: The number of RADIUS Disconnects not successful.

juniRadiusInitiatedRequestDisconnectNoSe.name: juniRadiusInitiatedRequestDisconnectNoSessionIds
juniRadiusInitiatedRequestDisconnectNoSe.description: The number of RADIUS Disconnect requests recieved from this client with no session-id present.

juniRadiusInitiatedRequestDisconnectBadA.name: juniRadiusInitiatedRequestDisconnectBadAuthenticators
juniRadiusInitiatedRequestDisconnectBadA.description: The number of RADIUS disconnect packets containing invalid authenticators received from this client.

juniRadiusInitiatedRequestDisconnectPack.name: juniRadiusInitiatedRequestDisconnectPacketsDropped
juniRadiusInitiatedRequestDisconnectPack.description: The number of RADIUS disconnect packets which were received from this client on the authentication port and dropped for some other reason.

juniRadiusInitiatedRequestCoaRequests.name: juniRadiusInitiatedRequestCoaRequests
juniRadiusInitiatedRequestCoaRequests.description: The number of RADIUS Change of Authorization packets received from this client.

juniRadiusInitiatedRequestCoaAccepts.name: juniRadiusInitiatedRequestCoaAccepts
juniRadiusInitiatedRequestCoaAccepts.description: The number of RADIUS Change of Authorization requests that were succesful.

juniRadiusInitiatedRequestCoaRejects.name: juniRadiusInitiatedRequestCoaRejects
juniRadiusInitiatedRequestCoaRejects.description: The number of RADIUS Change of Authorization requests that were not successful.

juniRadiusInitiatedRequestCoaNoSessionId.name: juniRadiusInitiatedRequestCoaNoSessionIds
juniRadiusInitiatedRequestCoaNoSessionId.description: The number of RADIUS Change of Authorization requests recieved from this client with no session-id present.

juniRadiusInitiatedRequestCoaBadAuthenti.name: juniRadiusInitiatedRequestCoaBadAuthenticators
juniRadiusInitiatedRequestCoaBadAuthenti.description: The number of RADIUS Change of Authorization packets containing invalid authenticators received from this client.

juniRadiusInitiatedRequestCoaPacketsDrop.name: juniRadiusInitiatedRequestCoaPacketsDropped
juniRadiusInitiatedRequestCoaPacketsDrop.description: The number of RADIUS Change of Authorization packets which were received from this client on the authentication port and dropped for some other reason.

juniRadiusInitiatedRequestCfgClientTable.name: juniRadiusInitiatedRequestCfgClientTable
juniRadiusInitiatedRequestCfgClientTable.description: The (conceptual) table listing the RADIUS initiated request clients with which the server shares a secret.

juniRadiusInitiatedRequestCfgClientEntry.name: juniRadiusInitiatedRequestCfgClientEntry
juniRadiusInitiatedRequestCfgClientEntry.description: An entry (conceptual row) representing a RADIUS authentication server with which the ERX shares a secret.

juniRadiusInitiatedRequestCfgClientAddre.name: juniRadiusInitiatedRequestCfgClientAddress
juniRadiusInitiatedRequestCfgClientAddre.description: The IP address of the RADIUS disconnect client referred to in this table entry.

juniRadiusInitiatedRequestCfgClientPortN.name: juniRadiusInitiatedRequestCfgClientPortNumber
juniRadiusInitiatedRequestCfgClientPortN.description: The UDP port the server is listening on to recieve requests from this client.

juniRadiusInitiatedRequestCfgKey.name: juniRadiusInitiatedRequestCfgKey
juniRadiusInitiatedRequestCfgKey.description: The secret (RADIUS authenticator) used by the serevr during exchanges with this client. The default is a zero-length string, indicating no authenticator is used.

juniRadiusInitiatedRequestCfgDisconnect.name: juniRadiusInitiatedRequestCfgDisconnect
juniRadiusInitiatedRequestCfgDisconnect.description: When enabled, RADIUS initiated disconnect requests are processed.

juniRadiusInitiatedRequestCfgChangeOfAut.name: juniRadiusInitiatedRequestCfgChangeOfAuthorization
juniRadiusInitiatedRequestCfgChangeOfAut.description: When enabled, RADIUS change of authorization requests are processed.

juniRadiusAuthInitiatedRequestCompliance.name: juniRadiusAuthInitiatedRequestCompliance
juniRadiusAuthInitiatedRequestCompliance.description: The compliance statement for entities which implement the Juniper RADIUS Initiated Request MIB.

juniRadiusInitiatedRequestGroup.name: juniRadiusInitiatedRequestGroup
juniRadiusInitiatedRequestGroup.description: The basic collection of objects providing management of RADIUS Initiated Request.
